Prompt 2.2.6: Add UI Components

**Objective**: Create reusable UI components.

**Instructions for AI Agent**:

Create basic UI components in src/components/ui/:

Button.astro:

Accept props: variant ('primary' | 'secondary' | 'outline'), size ('sm' | 'md' | 'lg'), href (optional)
Render as <button> or <a> based on href prop
Include slot for content

Variants:

primary: primary color background, white text
secondary: secondary color background, white text
outline: border only, transparent background


Sizes: appropriate padding for each size
Hover and active states
Disabled state


Input.astro:

Accept props: type, placeholder, name, value, required
Styled text input
Focus state with primary color border
Error state (red border)
Include label support


Modal.astro (for future login/register):

Overlay background
Centered content area
Close button
Slot for content
Styling: shadow, rounded corners, max width


SearchBar.astro:

Input field with search icon
Submit button or enter key support
Autocomplete dropdown area (empty for now)
Expand on focus animation
Clear button when text is entered



DELIVERABLE: Reusable UI components with consistent styling.